history.content:
Hi everyone!

Starting next Monday, April 13, HKN will be starting to host remote tutoring hours as a replacement for our in-person walk-in tutoring services. To facilitate this, we’ve started a Discord server moderated by HKN that will function as a virtual campus reading room, where you can study together, ask course advice, or just hang out! We created this Discord as a virtual environment for collaboration and community. 

 

On the server, feel free to: 

- Get tutoring help from an HKN officer 

- Study for midterms together 

- Socialize with others 

- Share your stress over a project

- Ask questions about concepts 

- Get advice about classes, research, jobs, etc. 

- Play League of Legends XOR Minecraft 

- And many more...

If you would like to join the server, please fill out this form: [We have closed off the Discord for the rest of the Spring 2020 semester]
We’ll process your join request as soon as possible and send you an invite link!


Hope everyone stays safe!
HKN Tutoring Committee
